com.djrapitops.nmplayer.messaging

Enum Phrase

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Phrase>
      • com.djrapitops.nmplayer.messaging.Phrase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Phrase>

    public enum Phrase
extends Enum<Phrase>
    This class is an Enum class containing all the messages used by the program.

    Main purpose of holding all messages in one place is to allow easy locale translation in the future.

    Messages can hold placeholders such as REPLACE0 or REPLACE1, and they will be replaced with given parameters for Phrase.parse(String...).

    Author:
    Rsl1122
    See Also:
    MessageSender
